{"tid":1218064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 買買下物資 比人掃場 渣都無","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:23:18.000Z","uid":151909,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa4f1af327330f3f8e271b1b0d6559fb18616c0b","tid":1218064,"uid":151909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"Sorry呃大家入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEVgCN3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEVgCN3.png&h=5d9a9186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但如果喺呢個時候<br />\n仲有人喺到做埋啲 同呃死人錢無分別既事<br />\n真係睇唔過睇<br />\n對鞋炒價7000幾<br />\n係咪想再賺多啲<br />\n就打埋句買物資用哂錢？<br />\n如果係既話 真係無野好講<br />\n大佬 打緊仗 可唔可以唔好做埋啲陰側野？<br />\n既然佢咁等錢洗 不如大家幫下佢<br />\n我諗如果唔等錢洗 都唔會做到咁<br />\n大家幫下佢 第一個利用呢件事搵錢既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96d2b6721d475a0bc8d8f80585054638eab7f3c","tid":1218064,"uid":38904,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"條友肯定冇去過買物資<br />\n有冇聽過人話自己捐晒啲錢去charity所以冇錢開飯?"},{"pid":"b46e7e1962bb5eeb0f2b367dea7379a16417d9e9","tid":1218064,"uid":258566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f413746195a579aa0af3fd214d284b5bf49172b","tid":1218064,"uid":151909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f96d2b6721d475a0bc8d8f80585054638eab7f3c","tid":1218064,"uid":38904,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"條友肯定冇去過買物資<br />\n有冇聽過人話自己捐晒啲錢去charity所以冇錢開飯?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:53:09.000Z","msg":"你唔好咁 <br />\n人地講到明有去買有去搬<br />\n我唔比你屈佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有心就幫下佢啦"},{"pid":"092ade95fa719c2bf560ad98f52b3075fcd6450c","tid":1218064,"uid":151909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b46e7e1962bb5eeb0f2b367dea7379a16417d9e9","tid":1218064,"uid":258566,"lik